        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">I've been looking for these forever for my monk as a pulling device.  They are very nice for Necro's as stated above, and amazing for monks as a pulling device.  </P><P>Btw, paying well for these on Rodcet Nife if anyone has for sale.  =P</P><P>-------------------------<BR>[47 Necromancer] Alluna Moonshadow (Erudite) <BR>Rodcet Nife<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
